For HBase client for java.
===============================
You  can use the following hbase client version for spark 2.3.1
Note: HBase-Spark integration libraries are provided in the HBase-3.0.0 which yet to release.

<dependency>
            <groupId>org.apache.hbase</groupId>
            <artifactId>hbase-client</artifactId>
            <version>1.2.4</version>
  </dependency>

<dependency>
            <groupId>org.apache.spark</groupId>
            <artifactId>spark-core_2.11</artifactId>
            <version>2.3.1</version>
        </dependency>
